If you dont wanna follow the rules then gtfo?[/quote]

I don’t like flaming but I will under any circumstance defend myself. Okay, so be quite clear here, I did search 2-4 topics and looked in the tutorials list thread for a duplicate thread. I found other ways to bypass the webmarshal. But not this way. I am not going to spend my time looking through 8 or however many pages just to try to contribute to this community, especially if this is what i’m going to get back.

I wouldn’t have gotten so upset had you said “There is already a topic for this, but thanks anyway” or something like that, but you came in here just plain rude. I did take the time out to read a page or two of your last post’s, which came out to mostly be spam or flame.

If you want to talk about rules, maybe you should read some yourself.

Rule 3:
We don’t make spelling mistakes on purpose. We use “you” not “u”, we use “why” not “y” etc.

Rule 6:
We respect each other and other communities. We don’t flame each other or other communities. We don’t fight on the forums.

I could continue flaming but I won’t.
